CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 13, reads: "Founders Day For Lambda - Founders Day was observed by Lambda Kappa Mu Sorority at the Ellis Hotel. A closed dinner party and program were held at the Shangri-La Room. Standing clockwise are Sorors Golden McCutcheon, Dolores Johnson, Georgianna Breyard, Grace McCray, Rose Wallace, Lorraine McCoad, and Maudelena Johnson.  Seated: Madeline Washington, Gladys Robinson, Cora Cooper-Basileus, Florence Purdue, and Peggy Freeman - Tennie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve Lambda Kappa Mu sorority members, standing from left: Golden McCutcheon, Dolores Johnson, Georgianna Breyard, Grace McCray, Rose Wallace, Lorraine McCoad, Maudelena Johnson; seated: Madeline Washington, Gladys Robinson, Cora Cooper-Basileus, Florence Purdue, and Peggy Freeman, gathered for Founders Day banquet at Shangri La room of Ellis Hotel
